    "body": "This issue that you describe is the one linked in the previous comment https://github.com/algolia/instantsearch.js/issues/5269. The workaround is to invert the order of the composition (first the `connectRefinementList`), you can see it in action in the [last comment](https://github.com/algolia/instantsearch.js/issues/5269) of the thread.",
